          <actionDate>2017-01-30</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill exempts from federal-aid highway vehicle weight limitations a vehicle operating on a segment of the Interstate System in North Dakota if it:</p> <ul> <li>has a gross vehicle weight of 129,000 pounds or less;</li> <li>complies with certain single axle, tandem axle, and bridge formula weight limits; and </li> <li>is authorized to operate on such segment under North Dakota law.</li> </ul>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
